1 address of the renter;
2 informing the renter of the termination or nonrenewal of the
3 rental agreement; and
4 (2) provides a renter not less than fifteen (15) days after the
5 owner delivers to the renter the written notice described in
6 subdivision (1) to remove all of the renter's personal property
7 from the rented space.
8 (e) A renter may not continue to use a storage space at the
9 self-service storage facility after the owner has delivered the
10 written notice described in subsection (d)(1).
11 (f) Prior to a former renter's removal of all of the former
12 renter's personal property from a self-service storage facility, but
13 after the owner has delivered the written notice described in
14 subsection (d)(1), the owner may place reasonable restrictions on
